    "intro": "Think of this as your grandmother's sathu maavu porridge, reborn as a cafe-style smoothie bowl. Frozen bananas blend with Wefeasto Health Mix and curd into something thick, cold and almost ice-cream-like. Pile on the toppings and breakfast suddenly looks like dessert.",
    "authorSub": "Breakfast recipe",
